# Documentation

- Code is source of truth; update docs with behavior changes.
- Label Implemented / Experimental / Planned / Unsafe for production.
- Do not describe roadmap features in present tense.
- Prefer accurate privacy wording (see `docs/architecture/PRIVACY_MODEL.md`).
- Point operators to `docs/audit/` and `PRODUCTION.md` for gaps.
- Env names must match code (`COMPUTE_PLUGIN_ALLOWLIST`, not `COMPUTE_ALLOWLIST`).
